1
00:00:05,900 --> 00:00:08,080
What will you do, father?

2
00:00:09,200 --> 00:00:12,400
You can no longer hide
behind the skirts of Athena.

3
00:00:12,540 --> 00:00:17,020
Athena is dead because of the
rage that consumes you, Kratos.

4
00:00:17,780 --> 00:00:19,500
What more will you destroy?

5
00:00:20,020 --> 00:00:22,300
The hands of death could not defeat me.

6
00:00:23,060 --> 00:00:26,340
The sisters of fate could not hold me.

7
00:00:26,341 --> 00:00:29,580
And you will not see the end of this day.

8
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:32,120
I will have my revenge!

9
00:00:32,480 --> 00:00:36,360
Excellent, child!
I will tolerate your insolence no more!

